      "message": "[Minor] Line 183: ProcessLifecycleOwner observer registration is unconditional in onCreate(). The comment says duplicate registration is prevented by reusing the same observer instance, but LifecycleRegistry does not make repeated addObserver calls on the same observer a safe no-op across custom/test initialization paths; duplicate registration can cause duplicate restore/deactivation scheduling. Guard registration with a boolean or move it to an initialization path that is guaranteed to run once.",
